  "content": "GIN GINS® GINGER CANDY GIN GINS® ORIGINAL GINGER CHEWS Bold, chewy and unmistakably ginger, these classic candies deliver the deep warmth and gentle tingle that true ginger lovers crave. No frills, no flavor twists, just pure ginger intensity in its most iconic form. If you appreciate ginger in its truest expression, this is where it begins. Made with 10% fresh ginger – more than any other brand Great for travel and nausea-related conditions Non-GMO | Gluten Free | Vegan America’s #1 selling ginger candy Voted “Best Candy” by the Fiery Foods Association Sweetened with cane sugar – nothing artificial Sustainably farmed ginger – locally grown near the candy factory Buy online or find it in the candy aisle at your local grocery or specialty store Voted “Best Candy” by the 2024 Fiery Foods Association Scovie Awards PRODUCT DETAILS NUTRITIONAL INFO MEET “THE ORIGINAL” MR. KNOBS It’s hard work being the mascot for the world’s best-loved ginger brand. Tired of running from paparazzi only to rush to photoshoots and interviews, Mr. Knobs loves nothing more than relaxing with a soothing ginger treat… Addictively Delicious I first encountered these chews back in the day at Walmart. While I don’t remember why I decided to try themShow more Response from The Ginger People US Thank you for your kind words, Blakely! We are so happy to hear how helpful (and delectable) our GIN GINS(r) Original ChewsShow more We Love GIN GINS! I wanted to take a moment to share how much GIN GINS have meant to my cousin. She has been battling multiple complexShow more THANK YOU!!! For the last 14 months, I have been plagued by severe intestinal discomfort and hypersensitivity. I have tried every form of diet modificationShow more Easy to find These are the easiest to find – they’re popping up at more and",
